            <h1>A Shared Space<br /> for the Next Generation</h1>
            <h2 class="subtitle">An interview with Hideaki Aoyama</h2>
            <h2 class="location"><a href="/spaces/aoyama-meguro/">Aoyama | Meguro</a>, Nakameguro</h2>
          </div>          
